<br>
This idea popped into my head awhile back.<br>
I haven't done a damned thing with it because I'm afraid of the massive amount of work that would go into a project like this...<br>
<br>
First of all, this would be done as a comic book. However, the comic pages would be imported into Macromedia Flash and the choices the reader makes determine which page they see next. It's like a &quot;Choose Your Own Adventure&quot; comic.<br>
<br>
The idea is that the title character <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>Lily</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END-->, has no fixed identity. She wakes up each morning with no clear memory of the day before. She can become anything. She's a 17 year old girl that always seems to wake up every morning in her room and has to decide what to do for the day.<br>
<br>
For example, Lily wakes up and has to decide what to wear. In her closet is a school uniform, a magic power ring, a .44 semi automatic pistol and a black dress. Pick one.<br>
<br>
Whatever choice Lily makes determines the genre of the story. If Lily were to choose the magic power ring, the story would take on a superhero slant, the pistol would be more hardcore, the school girl outfit would be more &quot;normal&quot; while the black dress could lead to romance.<br>
<br>
With MM Flash, Lily would be able to collect items, clues and even have arrtibute scores. Like a comic book game.<br>
<br>
I don't want to get too deep into the details at this point.<br>
Wha'cha think? <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub25.ezboard.com/bpolykarbonbbs.showUserPublicProfile?gid=otakulad>OtakuLad</A> at: 5/13/03 9:29:38 am<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#aaaaaa><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub25.ezboard.com/bpolykarbonbbs.showUserPublicProfile?gid=lomebririon>Lomebririon</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Pre-Karbonite</span><br> <font color=#336699>(5/6/03 2:33 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm40.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=29.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> RE: Lily Schizophrenic</span><hr size=1> That sounds GREAT!<!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :eek --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/eek.gif ALT=":eek"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
